title: Pose Episode 2 Access Review
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I loved Stan's explanation to Angel. He just wants one real thing in his life, which I think is two things - Angel herself obviously,  but also his feelings for her, as I believed they are genuine feelings and he really seems to be falling for her.
“It’s on the house” that’s Elsa Mars’ line from the diner in episode 1 of AHS: Freak Show!
Also Miss Elecktra played by Dominique Jackson was in a reality show called SLAY for transgender models. She is the sweetest person in real life
I love this show sooo much
The boy lounge actually existed here in NYC.
